<topic id="preferences-diff-appearance-EC">
  <title>Appearance Preferences</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Preferences<indexterm>Diff Appearance</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Diff appearance preferences</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>To configure the appearance options for the visual file comparison tool, go to
        <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol> (<uicontrol>Eclipse</uicontrol> on Mac OSX) and choose <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Preferences</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol keyref="product"/>
        <uicontrol>DIFF</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Appearance</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>. This preferences page includes the following sections and options:</p>
    <p>
      <dl>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Incoming color</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Specifies the color used on the vertical bar for incoming changes.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Outgoing color</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Specifies the color used on the vertical bar for outgoing changes.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Conflict color</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Specifies the color used on the vertical bar for conflicts between the compared
            files.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
  </body>
</topic>